    "Many explanations produced during the inference phase were irrelevant to the context of the brain teaser, indicating a failure to capture the reasoning path of most multiple-choice questions.",
    "In summary, both variations of Llama 2, despite their large scale, proved incapable of effectively understanding and reasoning through the multiple-choice questions provided.",
    "The Mistral-7b foot_6 model outperformed all others significantly.",
    "Prior to fine-tuning, we applied the QLoRA technique.",
    "Using a learning rate of 2e -5 and a batch size of 2, each model underwent finetuning for 250 steps using the train split of the subtasks' dataset."
